            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%AA%A8%E8%B4%A8%E7%96%8F%E6%9D%BE%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#世界骨质疏松日#</span></a>】人体骨密度在20-30岁达到峰值后，就会开始逐渐减少，因此年轻人也有可能会骨质疏松<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>！那哪些生活习惯容易引起骨质疏松？骨质疏松可逆吗？卫子今天就为大家说清！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>最后卫子告诫各位，不要仗着年轻拼命“作”，等老了才来后悔哦！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4694329315491843" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly8gvlldxf2dzj60zk0k040m02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/LoINdIFtlx07QJNpHt5m01041200Ning0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;trans_finger=1f0da16358befad33323e3a1b7f95f