            <description><![CDATA[宫颈癌所到之处真是令所有女性闻风丧胆<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[揣手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/af/2022_chuaishou_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>，那就拿它没辙了吗？有！打宫颈癌疫苗！到底什么是HPV？感染HPV一定会得宫颈癌？二价、四价、九价疫苗有啥区别？什么情况下不能打？这里全说清了👇🏻（卫子划个重点：哪种疫苗都能有效预防宫颈癌，所以，四价九价不重要，关键是能打趁早打！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[举手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fd/2022_raisehand_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1lmzlj20p014pq6l.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr2d3cxj20p01koagp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1mxiij20p014pdkh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1nictj20p017naf2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1ndimj20p012wae4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1qfzlj20p01q8aif.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1n5koj20p01cmdlg.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1mtwij20p015on28.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hj1kr1p8i9j20p01kyq9b.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
